  sources:
  - name: 4. Transport and Mobility | Cork City Council's Online Consultation 
      Portal
    authority: Cork City Council
    url: 
      https://consult.corkcity.ie/en/consultation/draft-cork-city-development-plan-2022-2028/chapter/4-transport-and-mobility
    description: 'Format: URL; Licensing: Publicly available; Geographic Coverage:
      Cork City; Date Last Updated: 2026-05-12 00:00:00; Updated by: Arup'
  - name: A REVIEW OF RESIDENTIAL HEAT DECARBONISATION IN IRELAND
    authority: ESRI; admin@esri.ie
    url: https://www.esri.ie/system/files/publications/QEC2026SPR_SA_Lynch.pdf
    description: 'Format: .pdf; Licensing: Publicly available; Geographic Coverage:
      National; Date Last Updated: 2026-05-12 00:00:00; Updated by: Arup'
  - name: Arup assumption
    authority: Arup
    url:
    description: 'Expert-judgement estimate made by Arup during the Calculation sheet
      build, not derived from an independent published report -- typically used where
      only an aggregate figure was available and a breakdown had to be assumed (e.g.
      splitting total on-road transport emissions across vehicle types by an assumed
      percentage).; Licensing: Internal; Geographic Coverage: Cork City; Update Frequency:
      Static; Date Last Updated: 2026-05-12 00:00:00; Updated by: Arup'
  - name: Bus and Rail Statistics for Ireland - Statistical Bulletin 2023
    authority: National Transport Authority (NTA); Dermot O’Gara; +353 0 1 
      8798346
    url: 
      https://www.nationaltransport.ie/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PSO-Bus-and-Rail-Statistics-Bulletins-2023_Nov24-7.11.24-V4.pdf
    description: 'Attachment: PSO-Bus-and-Rail-Statistics-Bulletins-2023_Nov24-7.11.24-V4.pdf;
      Format: .pdf; Licensing: Publicly available; Geographic Coverage: Cork City;
      Update Frequency: Annually; Date Last Updated: 2026-05-12 00:00:00; Updated
